      • getClipping

        java.awt.Insets getClipping()
        Returns the clipping values as percent ratio relatively to the image size. The clipping are returned as insets converted/scaled to 100000 (=100%).(以相对于图像大小的百分比比形式返回剪切值。剪辑以转换/缩放为100000（=100%）的插入形式返回。)
        Returns:
        the clipping rectangle, which is given in percent in relation to the image width/height(剪裁矩形，以相对于图像宽度/高度的百分比给出)
